<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205753>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Adult female Pseudaulacaspis pyrrosiae Hodgson & Łagowska, sp. n. Where A = small dorsal 2 - barred ducts; B = large dorsal 2 - barred ducts; C = dorsal view of posterior end of pygidium; D = ventral view of posterior end of pygidium; E = gland spine; F = variation in shape of median lobes; G = ventral microduct; H = ventral small 2 - barred duct; J = anterior spiracle, and K = antenna." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/205753/files/figure.png" ;
